  "prompt": "Where can I get a consistent high quality service for commercial cleaning in Bangalore?",
  "response": "When looking for a consistent, high-quality commercial cleaning service in Bangalore, it\u2019s essential to choose a reputable company with a proven track record. Here are some popular and reliable options:\n\n---\n\n### **1. ** **Urban Company (formerly UrbanClap)**\n   - **Overview**: One of the most trusted platforms for professional cleaning services, offering tailored solutions for commercial spaces.\n   - **Services**: Deep cleaning, carpet cleaning, pest control, and regular maintenance.\n   - **Why Choose**: Certified professionals, transparent pricing, and a user-friendly booking system.\n   - **Website**: [www.urbancompany.com](https://www.urbancompany.com)\n\n---\n\n### **2. ** **PurpleSlate Hospitality**\n   - **Overview**: A leading facility management company in Bangalore, specializing in commercial cleaning.\n   - **Services**: Housekeeping, janitorial services, and sanitation solutions.\n   - **Why Choose**: Customized plans, trained staff, and eco-friendly cleaning products.\n   - **Website**: [www.purpleslate.in](https://www.purpleslate.in)\n\n---\n\n### **3. ** **Servico Facility Management**\n   - **Overview**: Known for its comprehensive facility management and cleaning services.\n   - **Services**: Office cleaning, window cleaning, and after-event cleanup.\n   - **Why Choose**: Experienced team and commitment to hygiene standards.\n   - **Website**: [www.servicofm.com](http://www.servicofm.com)\n\n---\n\n### **4. ** **Alliance Facility Management Services (AFMS)**\n   - **Overview**: Offers reliable and high-quality cleaning services for various commercial spaces.\n   - **Services**: Regular cleaning, disinfection, and specialized cleaning.\n   - **Why Choose**: Focus on customer satisfaction and use of advanced cleaning equipment.\n   - **Website**: [www.afmsindia.com](http://www.afmsindia.com)\n\n---\n\n### **5. ** **Clean & Shine India**\n   - **Overview**: A professional cleaning service provider with a strong presence in Bangalore.\n   - **Services**: Office cleaning, upholstery cleaning, and post-construction cleaning.\n   - **Why Choose**: Affordable pricing and trained, vetted staff.\n   - **Website**: [www.cleanandshineindia.com](http://www.cleanandshineindia.com)\n\n---\n\n### **6. ** **HireMaid**\n   - **Overview**: A trusted name in Bangalore for cleaning services, including commercial spaces.\n   - **Services**: Daily cleaning, deep cleaning, and specialized services.\n   - **Why Choose**: Flexible packages and high-quality service.\n   - **Website**: [www.hiremaid.in](https://www.hiremaid.in)\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Service:**\n- Check reviews and testimonials from other businesses.\n- Ensure they use eco-friendly and safe cleaning products.\n- Verify if they offer customized plans for your specific needs.\n- Confirm their staff is trained and background-checked.\n\n---\n\nLet me know if you need help narrowing down your options!",
